Project Type.description: A string classifiying the project. Current;y supported values are Campaign, Task. PersonalProject and StudyProject.

Category.description: A user specified category name that can be used for example, to define product types or agreement types.

Identifier.description: A user asigned identifier.

Start Date.description: Project start date as an ISO 8601 string.

Planned End Date.description: Planned project end date as an ISO 8601 string.

Priority.description: An integer priority for the project.

Project Phase.description: A string describing the phase of the project.

Project Status.description: A string representing the project status.

Project Health.description: A string representing the health of the project.

Qualified Name.description: A unique qualified name for the element. Generated using the qualified name pattern  if not user specified.

Anchor Scope Name.description: An optional  anchor element focusing the search for this term. Often a glossary collection.

Merge Update.description: If true, only those attributes specified in the update will be updated; If false, any attributes not provided during the update will be set to None.

Additional Properties.description: Additional user defined values organized as name value pairs in a dictionary.

Extended Properties.description: Additional user defined values organized as name value pairs in a dictionary.

External Source GUID.description: Identifier of an external source that is associated with this element.

External Source Name.description: Name of an external element that is associated with this element.
